				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/B%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u-ng%C3%A2m/poem-4DAwE-zkYaCbjLMeL3c7mw">Bạch đầu ngâm - 白頭吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Huy%E1%BB%81n-Quang-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/C%C3%BAc-hoa-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-Ax4K3wOUF6ssYCNrcddLGA">Cúc hoa kỳ 1 - 菊花其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Huy%E1%BB%81n-Quang-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-ky6a-6Hq9AEiujrHK0DNTQ">Huyền Quang thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Huy%E1%BB%85n/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-li%E1%BB%85u-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-6/poem-vGrtq_q0LQtcXmiTKm8lLA">Dương liễu từ kỳ 6 - 柳枝辭其六</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Huy%E1%BB%85n/author-PbzSOCmqBMTC0GXwXGPRrw">Từ Huyễn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Giang-h%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-trung/poem-YOqcnbHcqlgaw19dt3ZKTQ">Đại Giang hương trung - 大江香中</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/author-n8TXz8ZnEQ2g7U6IvK74Vw">Nguyễn Trung Ngạn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Kh%C3%A1ch-c%E1%BB%B1u-qu%C3%A1n/poem-fzujtAUwuEC2SaRe5iYs8A">Khách cựu quán - 客舊館</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-Huy-B%C3%ADch/Quang-Li%E1%BB%87t-x%C3%A3-giang-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-ng%C3%A2m/poem-i0IyJo1Hghuv8GD0dM4sug">Quang Liệt xã giang thượng ngâm - 光烈社江上吟光</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-Huy-B%C3%ADch/author-IUtlhs85uNhJ4NvGicsgMg">Bùi Huy Bích</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/T%C3%A1ng-hoa-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-gA5JJaf5Xy6SshvZx4FFWg">Táng hoa từ - 葬花詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/Th%E1%BB%8B-ch%C3%BAng-II/poem-buXkmBqVo3P7TXtPxSMrIw">Thị chúng (II) - 示眾</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/Th%E1%BB%A9-v%E1%BA%ADn-Kh%E1%BB%95ng-Ngh%E1%BB%8B-Ph%E1%BB%A7-C%E1%BB%ADu-h%E1%BA%A1n-d%C4%A9-nhi-th%E1%BA%ADm-v%C5%A9-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-zhnD700DqXVlALBE9Dj1SQ">Thứ vận Khổng Nghị Phủ “Cửu hạn dĩ nhi thậm vũ” kỳ 3 - 次韻孔毅甫久旱已而甚雨其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%ABu-Vi%E1%BB%85n/%E1%BB%A8c-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-L%C6%B0-nh%E1%BB%8B-n%E1%BB%AF/poem-UUlvKpi0YJxC4BOTftjoUA">Ức Đồng Lư nhị nữ - 憶桐廬二女</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%ABu-Vi%E1%BB%85n/author-sRemHKkmYCdxkkHc58hcHA">Cừu Viễn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
